msgid "Secondary bloodstream infection (BSI)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "programStageSections/yhamIeNXB9y/DESCRIPTION"
msgid "Secondary BSI that is thought to be seeded from the SSI. A BSI can be attributed to a SSI if it occurs in a 17-day period that includes the day of infection (=first SSI symptoms), 3 days prior, and 13 days after. Follow-up for secondary BSI is not mandatory."
msgstr ""

