msgid "Secondary Bloodstream Infection (BSI)/Sepsis"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "programStageSections/yuWQcD6kSTz/DESCRIPTION"
msgid "Secondary BSI that is thought to be seeded from the NEC or it's complications (e.g.; peritonitis after perforation). A BSI can be attributed to a NEC if it occurs in a 17-day period that includes the day of infection (=first NEC symptoms), 3 days prior, and 13 days after. Follow-up for secondary BSI is not mandatory."
msgstr ""

